"title": "5138: bowing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5138: bowing",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An act of submission before something or someone deemed worthy of honour.</p>\n<h2>Bowing as an act of submission</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:6\">GEN 42:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:2\">2SA 1:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:9\">PSA 72:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:3\">GEN 33:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:26-Gen43:28\">GEN 43:26–43:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:8\">GEN 49:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod11:8\">EXO 11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:7\">EXO 18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:10\">RUT 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:36\">1SA 2:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:8\">1SA 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:23\">1SA 25:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:5\">2SA 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:28\">2SA 18:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:16\">1KI 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:21\">1CH 21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:23\">ISA 49:23</a></p>\n<h2>Bowing before angels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:2\">GEN 18:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:1\">GEN 19:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:31\">NUM 22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:5\">LUK 24:5</a></p>\n<h2>Bowing before God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:31\">EXO 4:31</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:18\">2CH 20:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6\">PSA 95:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:3\">GEN 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:26\">GEN 24:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:27\">EXO 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:8\">EXO 34:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:10\">DEU 26:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:3\">DEU 33:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:47\">1KI 1:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:36\">2KI 17:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:20\">1CH 29:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:28\">2CH 29:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:6\">NEH 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:27\">PSA 22:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:23\">ISA 66:23</a></p>\n<h2>Bowing before the temple</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:7\">PSA 5:7</a></strong> <em>The temple represented God's presence.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:2\">PSA 138:2</a></p>\n<h2>Bowing before idols</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:8\">EXO 32:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:16\">2KI 17:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:8\">ISA 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:2\">NUM 25:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:26\">DEU 29:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:3\">2KI 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:14\">2CH 25:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:17\">ISA 44:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:19\">ISA 44:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:16\">EZK 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:13\">MIC 5:13</a></p>\n<h2>Bowing before Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:11\">MAT 2:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:10\">PHP 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:2\">MAT 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:18\">MAT 9:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:25\">MAT 15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:29\">MAT 27:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:6\">MRK 5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17\">MRK 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:16\">LUK 17:16</a></p>\n<h2>Bowing as an expression of sorrow</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:14\">PSA 35:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:14\">PSA 145:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:6\">PSA 38:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:6\">PSA 57:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:8\">PSA 146:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:10\">LAM 2:10</a></p>",
